These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bike, jet-ski, snowmobile
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Transport   | jet-ski | bike | boat | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, pop, dubstep, classical
1. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
2. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | dubstep | pop | classical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, yellow, white, emerald
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Color   | white | aquamarine | yellow | emerald |

